        "16376331517629f95c-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A steadily growing team – mostly woman. <br/>Even though we don’t focus on a woman only team, we just happened to be one (almost). Everyone of us has a super power and all of them combined makes us quite strong. <br/>Before we introduce everyone of the team, let us share our values and beliefs with you. <br/></p>"
          }
        },
