    "16376331551fc06fea": {
      "type": "testimonial",
      "disabled": true,
      "blocks": {
        "163763315583f5288c-0": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1.png",
            "title1": "Kindness",
            "text1": "<p>We believe in being kind. <br/>Kind to other human beings and to animals. <br/>You never know what the person in front of you has experienced. We try to always assume the best and to give more than we take.</p>"
          }
        },
        "07f491ba-901b-46ee-a8a0-c8b55c2dc13d": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2.png",
            "title1": "Responsibility",
            "text1": "<p>Every single decision we make has to be made with the big picture in our head. <br/>We don’t think „but others don’t“ – we rather think ‚what if we all…?“</p>"
          }
        },
        "d065af5c-75c6-46ee-93fd-ee05e333d7e2": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3.png",
            "title1": "Honesty & Transparent",
            "text1": "<p>We are humans. We make mistakes. <br/>We believe in honesty and transparency. Every choice we make we made for a reason and we are happy to share. <br/>And we are also okay with saying „We made a mistake“. This is us.</p>"
          }
        },
        "c1790f4b-97ac-48a7-8b24-e6d7144d870d": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Website-Icons-09_1_1.png",
            "title1": "The power of many",
            "text1": "<p>We believe in collaboration, in exchange, in discussions. <br/>You got feedback for us? Please let us know! <br/>You would like to talk about an idea: Yeah for sure! <br/>If we all stick to our own business, we can’t grown and learn from each other. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
