    "16376614569279c52d": {
      "type": "team",
      "blocks": {
        "16376614560afea2c8-0": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/annika.jpg",
            "title1": "Annika (Founder)",
            "text1": "<p>With her background in design and marketing and with being the swiss army knife, she kickstarts ideas. <br/><br/>Superpowers: <br/>Multitasking at its best<br/><br/>Favorite thing to do within the company: <br/>Coming up with new product ideas</p>"
          }
        },
        "02fd9a62-751a-4a73-ae38-ac27e99a4739": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/devy.jpg",
            "title1": "Devy (Operations manager)",
            "text1": "<p>Devy has been the first employee and knows every single bit of the company. <br/>She knows the history, she was there when the first collar was born and keeps the whole company on track.<br/><br/>Superpowers:<br/>Numbers and excel sheets</p>"
          }
        },
        "096bf40d-7d59-4824-a536-806cc3394216": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/maya.jpg",
            "title1": "Maya (Designer)",
            "text1": "<p>Maya makes everything pretty in this company. All the cute little icons and graphics are her work. <br/>No project is too difficult and her favorit sentence is: „let me try!“<br/><br/>Superpowers: <br/>Magically make everything look good</p>"
          }
        },
        "e389cb17-9ee0-467a-9237-70753318b8fc": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/lania_131e6e39-76d9-4815-b745-d223b3f10558.jpg",
            "title1": "Lania (Production Manager)",
            "text1": "<p>Lanias experience is in production and quality control. Her eyes won’t ever miss anything.<br/>We secretly think, she can see nano-meters. <br/><br/>Superpowers:<br/>Eyes of an eagle</p>"
          }
        },
        "865b1930-dcb9-468f-88af-1b4baaa01f29": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/lilis.jpg",
            "title1": "Lilis   (Operations Assistant)",
            "text1": "<p>Lilis  is our good soul and always there when we need an extra hand. She supports Devy with the company operations and makes sure Kali gets enough pets. <br/><br/>Superpowers:<br/>Makes everyone feel better</p>"
          }
        },
        "90aefa5e-4b8a-4936-8b48-2bb20575cc8e": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Kali.jpg",
            "title1": "Kali (Secret Boss)",
            "text1": "<p>Kali is the secret boss of the company. She tests the products but actually doesn’t work. Her presence is all that we get.<br/><br/>Superpowers:<br/>Sleeping more than 20hrs per day<br/><br/>Favorite thing to do within the company: <br/>Getting the pets!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
